## Architecture Decisions

### Dictionary Integration

External API calls are isolated inside
services/dictionary.service.js
to keep controllers clean.

### Review Scheduling

Needs Work:
- 1 day

Got It Right:
- 3 days

### Dev Mode

Needs Work:
- 1 minute

Got It Right:
- 3 minutes

This allows reviewers to test
the full review lifecycle in under
5 minutes.

### MongoDB Query

Words due for review:

{
  nextReviewDate: {
    $lte: new Date()
  }
}